org.colomoto.biolqm.io.antlr

Class ExpressionStack

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.colomoto.biolqm.io.antlr.ExpressionStack

  • public class ExpressionStack
extends Object
    Stack to reconstruct a parsed logical expression. This takes a series of "signal" denoting operands and operators (sent by the parser) and constructs a proper logical function tree from it. It handles the shared parts of function parsing from different formats.
    Author:
    Aurelien Naldi
